{"id":"678fe4a4906c7bd23722c71f","typeName":"AssaultRifle","category":"weapon","parentTypeChain":["AssaultRifle","Weapon","CompoundItem","Item"],"handbook":{"categoryId":null,"price":0},"common":{"name":{"zh":"AN-94 5.45x39 突击步枪","en":"AN-94 5.45x39 assault rifle"},"shortName":{"zh":"AN-94","en":"AN-94"},"description":{"zh":"AN-94步枪旨在作为俄军现役AK-74系列步枪的潜在替代品。由于结构复杂且造价高昂，该枪未能实现全面取代AK-74的预期目标，目前仅作为特种武器有限列装。AN-94具备独特的延迟后坐力机制，前两发子弹的射击后坐感会延后出现，从而提升恶劣作战环境下的命中率。该枪还拥有每分钟1800发射速的特殊两连发功能，次发弹与首发弹的射击间隔极短，此特性常被称为\"超爆发\"机制。","en":"The AN-94 was designed as a potential replacement to the AK-74 series of rifles currently in service with the Russian Armed Forces. Due to its complex design and expense, it failed to fill its intended role as a replacement for the AK-74, but it is in limited use as a special purpose weapon. The AN-94 has the unique feature of delaying felt recoil for the first two rounds. This increases hit probability in adverse combat conditions. The AN-94 offers a unique two-shot burst function at a stated 1800 rounds per minute, with the second shot firing very close to the first round. This feature is often known as the hyperburst mechanism."},"weight":2.9,"width":4,"height":1,"rarity":"Rare","backgroundColor":"black"},"properties":{"_raw":{"AdjustCollimatorsToTrajectory":false,"AimPlane":0.19,"AimSensitivity":0.65,"AllowFeed":true,"AllowJam":true,"AllowMisfire":true,"AllowOverheat":true,"AllowSlide":true,"AnimationVariantsNumber":0,"BackgroundColor":"black","BaseMalfunctionChance":0.1771,"BoltAction":false,"BurstShotsCount":2,"CameraSnap":3.5,"CameraToWeaponAngleSpeedRange":{"x":0.1,"y":0.2,"z":0},"CameraToWeaponAngleStep":0.1,"CanPutIntoDuringTheRaid":true,"CanQueueSecondShot":true,"CanRequireOnRagfair":false,"CanSellOnRagfair":true,"CanUnloadAmmoByPlayer":true,"CantRemoveFromSlotsDuringRaid":[],"CenterOfImpact":0.055,"Chambers":[{"_id":"5ac4cd105acfc4001633985b","_mergeSlotWithChildren":false,"_name":"patron_in_weapon","_parent":"5ac4cd105acfc40016339859","_props"